description:
## HIGH — Create the plan data structure and navigation entry point

### Source doc
`/Users/pratham/Downloads/2_week_indian_cooking_beginner_plan.md` — Contains the full 14-day plan with daily titles, goals, ingredients, instructions, and skills learned.

### What's wrong
There's no data model for the 2-week Indian cooking plan and no way to navigate to it.

### What to build

**1. Create `lib/indian-plan-data.ts`**

This file defines the full 14-day plan structure with typed interfaces. Each day maps to a recipe ID and includes metadata from the doc.

```ts
export interface PlanDay {
  day: number;
  title: string;
  subtitle: string;
  recipeId: string;
  goals: string[];
  skillsLearned: string[];
  isAssemblyDay?: boolean;
}

export interface PlanWeek {
  week: number;
  title: string;
  focus: string;
  days: PlanDay[];
}

